#: 01001:9
msgid ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"Noooo!\n"
"Somebody help me!!\""
msgstr ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"¡No...!\n"
"¡¡Que alguien me ayude!!\""

#: 01001:14
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"Deh-heh-heh! What's wrong, girlie? Why don't you come with me?\""
msgstr ""

#: 01001:15
msgid "Pierre was attacking Sakura. She tried to run away, but he was persistently pursuing her."
msgstr ""

#: 01001:21
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Guys, please help with the cleaning.\""
msgstr ""

#: 01001:22
msgid ""
"After-school cleaning time.\n"
"Fujisaki-san's the only one who's actually making an effort."
msgstr ""
"Hora de la limpieza de después de clases.\n"
"Rin es la única que está haciendo bien el trabajo."

#: 01001:29
msgid ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"No! Help! Somebody help!!\""
msgstr ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"¡¡Que alguien me ayude!!\""

#: 01001:32
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"Scream all you want, no one's coming. Now give in and become mine!\""
msgstr ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"Nadie puede oírte. ¡Ríndete y sé mía!\""

#: 01001:33
msgid ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"Help!!\""
msgstr ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"¡¡Ayuda...!!\""

#: 01001:37
msgid ""
"{???}\n"
"\"Hold it right there!!\""
msgstr ""
"{???}\n"
"\"¡¡Déjala tranquila!!\""

#: 01001:38
msgid "A valiant voice responded to Sakura's scream for help."
msgstr "Alguien respondió al grito de Sakura."

#: 01001:41
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"Who is it!?\""
msgstr ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"¿¡Quién es!?\""

#: 01001:43
msgid ""
"{???}\n"
"\"Here I come!!\""
msgstr ""
"{???}\n"
"\"¡¡Allá voy!!\""

#: 01001:46
msgid "Appo came somersaulting onto the scene."
msgstr "Era Appo-."

#: 01001:48
msgid "*roll roll roll roll*"
msgstr "*Appo- rodando por el suelo*"

#: 01001:49
msgid "He rolled a few extra spins across the floor."
msgstr "Está rodando por el suelo."

#: 01001:53
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Stop me!\""
msgstr ""

#: 01001:57
msgid ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"Keep it together.\""
msgstr ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"¿Estás bien?\""

#: 01001:62
msgid "Daigo helped Appo to get up."
msgstr ""

#: 01001:63
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"You suck, Appo.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Eres penoso, Appo-.\""

#: 01001:66
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Shut up!\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"¡A callar!\""

#: 01001:70
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"Hey, who are you!\""
msgstr ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"¿¡Quién eres tú!?\""

#: 01001:75
msgid "Pierre and Appo squared off."
msgstr "Pierre y Appo- se encaran."

#: 01001:78
# El hombre de la alquimia.
# ¿El hombre alquímico? ¿Alquémico?
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"I am the defender of justice, Alchemy Man!\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"Soy...\n"
"¡El hombre alquémico!\""

#: 01001:82
msgid "He made a fighting pose with his hands together above his head. I think he was going for the character for 'gold'."
msgstr "En esta ocasión hasta ha puesto una pose de batalla."

#: 01001:85
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"You're the legendary Alchemy Man?\""
msgstr ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"¿¡Eres tú el legendario hombre alquémico!?\""

#: 01001:88
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Yes, I am! I'm here to vanquish you with my alchemy! Alchemy Charge!\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"¡Sí, soy yo!\n"
"¡¡Y estoy aquí para salvar el mundo!!\""

#: 01001:90
msgid "Shakiiiin!"
msgstr ""

#: 01001:94
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Gold La Esperma!\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"¡¡Rayo dorado!!\""

#: 01001:96
msgid "Kaboom!"
msgstr ""

#: 01001:98
msgid "An invisible laser shot from Appo's extended palms."
msgstr "El rayo se supone que salía de sus manos."

#: 01001:104
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"Gaaah!!\""
msgstr ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"¡¡No...!!\""

#: 01001:107
msgid "Pierre died."
msgstr "Pierre murió."

#: 01001:110
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Evil has been vanquished. You're safe now, little girl!\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"He erradicado el mal.\n"
"Pequeña, ¡ya estás a salvo!\""

#: 01001:115
msgid ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"...Little girl?\""
msgstr ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"¿Pequeña?\""

#: 01001:116
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"Alchemy Man is a defender of little girls!!\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"¡¡El hombre alquémico!!\""

#: 01001:122
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Please everyone, let's clean.\""
msgstr ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Venga... Limpiad, por favor...\""

#: 01001:123
msgid "Fujisaki-san was about to cry."
msgstr "Rin estaba ya casi llorando."

#: 01001:130
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"What are you guys doing?\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"¿Qué estáis haciendo?\""

#: 01001:131
msgid "Haruka had been watching the whole thing from the doorway, but she was too overwhelmed by our curious show to enter."
msgstr "Haruka estaba mirando el espectáculo junto a la puerta."

#: 01001:132
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"It's alright to come in. Evil has been vanquished.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Pasa, Haruka.\""

#: 01001:133
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Huh? Well, thanks I guess.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Gracias.\""

#: 01001:134
msgid "Haruka is visiting us again."
msgstr "Haruka ha venido a visitarnos otra vez."

#: 01001:139
msgid ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"Harunyan!\n"
"Do you wanna play Alchemy Man with us?\""
msgstr ""
"{Sakura}\n"
"\"¡Haruka!\n"
"¡¿Juegas con nosotros al hombre alquémico?!\""

#: 01001:142
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"What's Alchemy Man?\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"¿Qué es eso del 'hombre alquémico'?\""

#: 01001:149
msgid ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"A hero of justice who uses alchemy to save the world! ...At least that's the setting.\""
msgstr ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"Un héroe que usa la alquimia para salvar el mundo...\""

#: 01001:152
# Suena bien.
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Wow, you're using alchemy to fight evil? That sounds cool!\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Suena guay.\""

#: 01001:153
msgid "I can't believe she's showing genuine interest in this..."
msgstr "No puedo creer que le haya llamado la atención."

#: 01001:154
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"We're really feeling the alchemy's influence.\""
msgstr ""

#: 01001:159
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Really!?\n"
"You guys liked it?\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"¿¡De verdad!?\n"
"¿Os gusta?\""

#: 01001:160
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Sure.\n"
"It's cool. Just like magic.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Claro.\n"
"Mola. Es como la magia.\""

#: 01001:161
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Well, it's not really magic.\n"
"But I'm still glad you guys liked it.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Bueno. No es exáctamente como la magia,\n"
"pero aún así me alegro de que os guste.\""

#: 01001:166
msgid ""
"{Fuusen}\n"
"\"It's not worth getting worked up about, Haruka-chan.\n"
"Now they're even more annoying than ever.\""
msgstr ""

#: 01001:170
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"You guys are annoying!\""
msgstr ""

#: 01001:174
msgid ""
"{Andou}\n"
"\"A defender of justice who speaks like that? How low.\""
msgstr ""
"{Rei}\n"
"\"Un héroe nunca diría algo así.\""

#: 01001:175
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"You two are the bad guys!\n"
"Do you want me to defeat you with my Gold Anus Cutter?!\""
msgstr ""

#: 01001:178
msgid ""
"{Andou}\n"
"\"What? You want a go?\""
msgstr ""

#: 01001:182
msgid "Big Rei stood up to fight Alchemy Man."
msgstr "La Gran Rei se levantó para luchar al hombre alquémico."

#: 01001:183
msgid "She's huge. I could barely stand."
msgstr "Es enorme."

#: 01001:188
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Don't fight!\n"
"Come on, let's all join in and play Alchemy Man.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"¡No luchéis!\n"
"¡Juguemos todos al hombre alquémico!\""

#: 01001:192
msgid ""
"{Fuusen}\n"
"\"Us too?\n"
"No way!\""
msgstr ""
"{Hu-sen}\n"
"\"¿Nosotras también?\n"
"Ni hablar.\""

#: 01001:195
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Come on, it'll be fun!\n"
"This time Kazuko-chan can be the heroine!\""
msgstr ""

#: 01001:202
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"What!?\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"¿¡Qué!?\""

#: 01001:206
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"That's a bit rough.\""
msgstr ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"No funcionaría.\""

#: 01001:207
# "The only one" que comentan en el opening.
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"It'll be fine. Kazuko's perfect for the role. She's like a princess!\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"¡Ella es la única!\n"
"¡Es como una princesa!\""

#: 01001:211
msgid ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"A princess......\""
msgstr ""
"{Daigo}\n"
"\"Una princesa...\""

#: 01001:212
msgid ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"Are you insane?\""
msgstr ""
"{Pierre}\n"
"\"¿Estás de guasa?\""

#: 01001:213
msgid "At first, I thought Haruka was making fun of Fuusen."
msgstr "Al principio pensaba que Haruka estaba tomándole el pelo a Hu-sen."

#: 01001:219
msgid ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"The fact that she can honestly say that is part of what makes Haruka amazing.\""
msgstr ""
"{Ran}\n"
"\"Haruka parece decirlo en serio.\""

#: 01001:220
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I agree.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Pues sí.\""

#: 01001:221
msgid "Indeed, for some reason, Haruka saw Fuusen as extremely princess-like."
msgstr "De hecho, parece que por algún motivo Haruka ve a Hu-sen como alguna especie de princesa."

#: 01001:226
msgid ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"See? Kazuko doesn't seem to mind either.\""
msgstr ""
"{Mizuki}\n"
"\"A Hu-sen parece que no le importa.\""

#: 01001:231
msgid ""
"{Fuusen}\n"
"\"Fine, I'll do it. But I'm not doing this because of you boys. I'm just a girl who can't say no.\""
msgstr ""

#: 01001:232
msgid "It was true. She was totally in to it."
msgstr ""

#: 01001:237
msgid ""
"{Andou}\n"
"\"Hey, Villain, hurry up and kidnap Kazuko-chan.\""
msgstr ""
"{Rei}\n"
"\"Ey, malotes.\n"
"Capturad a la princesa Hu-sen.\""

#: 01001:238
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Huh? Me, the villain?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Yo? ¿'Malote'?\""

#: 01001:239
msgid "Why do I have to kidnap Fuusen?"
msgstr "¿Por qué me han metido en el grupo de los malos?"

#: 01001:246
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Then I'll be a villain along with Kazushi-kun! Kazushi-kun, I'm going to kidnap Kazuko-chan!\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"¡Yo también quiero ser de las malas!\n"
"¡Voy a secuestrar a Hu-sen!\""

#: 01001:247
msgid ""
"It's funny.\n"
"When Haruka takes over on something it's impossible to argue."
msgstr ""

#: 01001:248
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"All right, let's do it!\""
msgstr ""

#: 01001:249
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Kazuko-chan, I'm coming after you!!\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"¡¡Hu-sen, voy a atraparte!!\""

#: 01001:256
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Ah, hey, Appo-kun, hurry, save Kazuko-chan.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Venga Appo-, se supone que tienes que salvar a la princesa Hu-sen.\""

#: 01001:257
msgid ""
"{Appo}\n"
"\"S-sure!\""
msgstr ""
"{Appo-}\n"
"\"S-Sí.\""

#: 01001:258
msgid "Appo set off to reluctantly save the princess."
msgstr ""

#: 01001:264
msgid ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"Please, everyone, help clean...\""
msgstr ""
"{Rin}\n"
"\"¿Y qué pasa con la limpieza de la clase?\""

#: 01001:265
msgid "We ended up not doing our afternoon cleaning."
msgstr "Al final acabamos por no limpiar nada."

#: 01001:273
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"I had so much fun.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Me lo he pasado muy bien.\""

#: 01001:274
msgid "I'm escorting Haruka back to the dorm."
msgstr ""

#: 01001:275
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I feel bad for Fujisaki-san.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Me sabe mal por Rin.\""

#: 01001:278
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"That's true.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Es verdad.\""

#: 01001:279
# ¿Rei o Rin?
msgid "Since we refused to listen no matter how often she asked, Fujisaki-san ended up doing all the cleaning by herself."
msgstr "Rei acabó limpiando todo ella sola."

#: 01001:280
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"She should've joined us.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Debería haber jugado con nosotros.\""

#: 01001:281
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"That's true.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Es cierto.\""

#: 01001:284
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"By the way, I'm truly happy that you guys liked alchemy class so much. It takes a load off my mind.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Por cierto. De verdad que estoy muy contenta de que os haya gustado la alquimia.\""

#: 01001:285
msgid "I could see how relieved she was."
msgstr "Parece aliviada."

#: 01001:286
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I didn't know you were so worried about it.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"No sabía que te preocupase tanto.\""

#: 01001:289
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Well, I had no idea what sort of thing big city boys would like. All city people play internet or match-making site, right?\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Porque no tenía ni idea de cómo serían los chicos de la gran ciudad.\""

#: 01001:290
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Do you even know what those are?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿Pensabas que no iba a interesarnos la alquimia?\""

#: 01001:293
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Of course not. I was born and raised on this island. That's why I was worried you might find alchemy boring and old-fashioned.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Me preocupaba que a los chicos de la gran ciudad la alquimia les resultase arcaica, sosa y aburrida.\""

#: 01001:294
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I see.\n"
"But I guess you worried too much. We all liked it.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Ya veo.\n"
"Pero creo que te has preocupado demasiado. Nos ha gustado a toos.\""

#: 01001:297
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"I'm glad you all liked it. I'm glad you took an interest in it too, Kazushi-kun.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Y yo me alegro de que te gustase.\""

#: 01001:298
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Me?\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"¿A mí?\""

#: 01001:299
msgid ""
"I think she's starting to look at me as more than just a friend.\n"
"...Does that mean she has feelings for me?"
msgstr "Creo que me ve como algo más que un simple amigo... ¿Siente algo por mí?"

#: 01001:300
msgid "......Maybe I'm dreaming."
msgstr "Quizá esté soñando..."

#: 01001:303
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Hey, how come you didn't get to be Alchemy Man?\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Oye, ¿y cómo es que no hiciste tú de hombre alquémico?\""

#: 01001:304
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I was always told to be a bad guy.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Siempre hacía de chico malo.\""

#: 01001:305
msgid "Appo and Pierre always make sure they're the lead."
msgstr "Y Appo- y Pierre siempre hacían de buenos."

#: 01001:308
# Ay that me lol.
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Will you be Alchemy Man for me if I need help?\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"¿Y tú serás mi hombre alquémico cuando necesite ayuda?\""

#: 01001:309
msgid "I wonder... is she just being nice, or is she serious?"
msgstr "Me pregunto si lo ha dicho simplemente por ser amable, o si le gusto."

#: 01001:310
msgid "Either way, it was strange how she made me feel like doing it."
msgstr "Sea como fuere, me alegro de ahora que seamos buenos amigos."

#: 01001:311
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Yeah, you can count on me.\""
msgstr ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"Claro.\""

#: 01001:312
msgid ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Okay, I will.\""
msgstr ""
"{Haruka}\n"
"\"Ven a rescatarme.\""

#: 01001:313
# Desearía ser/Ojalá pueda|pudiera/Me encantaría ser tu héroe.
msgid "Alchemy Man, huh? I wonder if even I can ever be somebody's hero."
msgstr "Me encantaría ser tu héroe."
